Average temp by month

climate$Tavg <- (climate$tmin+climate$tmax)/2
boxplot(climate$Tavg~climate$month,
        xlab ="Month", ylab = "Temperature", main = "Temperature by Month, 1942-2016")

Precip by season

climate$season <- ifelse(climate$month %in% c(12,1,2), "Winter",
                         ifelse(climate$month %in% c(3,4,5), "Spring",
                                ifelse(climate$month %in% c(6,7,8), "Summer", "Fall")))
boxplot(climate$rain~climate$season)

Temperature by Month,1942-2016 (C)

climate$Tavg <- (climate$tmin+climate$tmax)/2
boxplot(climate$Tavg~climate$season)
